[src:smoothed-particle-hydrodynamics/smoothed-particle-hydrodynamics] Often in astrophysics, one wishes to model self-gravity in addition to pure hydrodynamics.
[src:smoothed-particle-hydrodynamics/smoothed-particle-hydrodynamics] The particle-based nature of SPH makes it ideal to combine with a particle-based gravity solver, for instance tree gravity code, particle mesh, or particle-particle particle-mesh.
